##22 villagers in Hubei who accidentally ate disinfectant tablets say they are fine

The papernews

The function introduction, has the connotation the current politics new media

CCTV news

According to CCTV news, the Government of the People's Republic of China in Huangmei town, Huangmei County, released the news on March 1: At about 9:30 a.m. on February 28, huangmei town Xiangyao village, a group of villagers 14 households 22 people mistakenly eat the town epidemic prevention and control headquarters issued by the dioxidochlorine(.) Environmental disinfection tablets (commonly known as "effervescent tablets") , the dose of a grain per person, after the emergency sent to the county people's Hospital. Six of the 22 were reported to have vomited when they felt unwell after swallowing. So far, 22 people have been treated.

REPORTER: Wei Fan, editor: Zhang Lin, video source: Relevant Person, Network Editor: Lee Re

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
After investigation, February 25, Huangmei town to the village community distribution of protective materials, have explained clearly the use of effervescent tablets and the use of 2 kg of water per tablet effervescent tablets, for household spraying disinfection. Village Women Director, Accountant Luo Xiaohong and grid member Zhai Jinxia are responsible for distributing supplies to the teams. At about 15:00 on the 27th, Luo Xiaohong called a group leader, Jiang Jianjun, to the village committee to collect a group of protective materials and distribute them to the villagers. Jiang Jianjun in the group to do epidemic prevention and persuasion work, then phone the village volunteers Jiang Jinxiong to the village committee to get. So Jiang Jinxiong to the village committee from Luo Xiaohong will be a group of protective materials. Luo Xiaohong explained to Jiang Jinxiong effervescent tablets are used for disinfection after mixing with water, 5 tablets per family. After receiving the protective materials, Jiang gave them to Jiang Jianjun at the home of a group of villagers, Jiang Yanan. Jiang Jinxiong believes that the material is Jiang Jianjun informed him from the village committee, should be clear about the use of materials and methods, then did not explain to Jiang Jianjun effervescent tablets use and methods.

At about 9:30 on the 28th, Jiang Jianjun, a group leader in Xiangyao village, Huangmei town, Huangmei County, led the village volunteers, Yu Qiao, Jiang Bing and Jiang Yongxin, as they went door to door for temperature tests, registration and distribution of effervescent tablets, jiang Jianjun thought effervescent tablets were a drug to prevent and treat the new coronavirus without knowing the purpose and method of use. He told villagers to "take one tablet each and swallow it" . Some of the villagers who had swallowed the effervescent tablets reported feeling unwell, jiang Jianjun promptly took back the effervescent tablets he had been given. After that news, the town, village cadres immediately rushed to the scene, will swallow the effervescent tablets of the villagers sent to the county people's Hospital for treatment. County Party Committee and county government leaders rushed to the hospital at the first opportunity to arrange the deployment of rescue work.

County People's Hospital set up the first time by the Party secretary, President, business president, medical unit chief, director of Digestive Medicine Department, Neurology Department director, director of cardiology department, head of cardiology department nurse, and other 8-person rescue special class. At present, through egg white + milk neutralization, gastric juice diversion, infusion of supplementary energy, 24-hour monitor monitoring, regular temperature measurement, examination and other means, 22 people admitted to the hospital in stable physical condition, there is no life-threatening, and arranged for the care of patients'family members, twenty-one of them are expected to be discharged on 2 March, while one will remain in the hospital for observation and treatment due to old age and other medical conditions.

Huangmei town said it would draw inspiration from the past and carry out comprehensive rectification. We will strictly manage the distribution and use of materials for prevention and control, carry out training on the distribution and use of materials for prevention and control in an all-round way, conduct a check on the distribution and use of drugs for prevention and control throughout the town, and ensure that disinfection supplies are placed separately and that village cadres are given special management, post the name and use method on the package of disinfection supplies to ensure the proper use and safe use of disinfection materials.

This issue is edited by Chang Chen
